data.text: @SenatorCantwell @GonzagaU Negotiating with the Islamic Republic legitimizes a regime sustained by mass killings, repression, and terror. The IRGC is already designated—any deal only endangers human rights and global security. Stand with the Iranian people; they want regime change.
@SenatorCantwell @GonzagaU You are a disgrace to our great state.
@SenatorCantwell @GonzagaU VOTE FOR THE SAVE ACT. DO YOUR JOB!! I voted for this and I did not vote for you and so did everyone else. You couldn’t win an election without cheating!!!
@SenatorCantwell @GonzagaU Shut up you anti American piece of shit

@SenatorCantwell @GonzagaU The world learned too late that Hitler wasn’t dangerous because of weapons alone, but because warnings were ignored. Limiting Iran’s nukes while legitimizing its terror network repeats the same mistake. Appeasement always fails.

@SenatorCantwell @GonzagaU Senator Cantwell, the people of Iran don’t want reforms or another nuclear deal - we need regime change. No negotiations with a regime that slaughters its own people. With U.S. support, Iranians can end this and restore regional stability. @PahlaviReza is the transitional leader.
